《'''闯堂兔2：疯狂马戏团'''》（{{lang-en|''Brave Rabbit 2: Crazy Circus''}}）是中国大陆3D动画电影，导演和编剧是曾宪林，配音包括[[小连杀|小连杀]]、[[叮当|叮当]]、[[郝祥海|郝祥海]]、[[王幸|王幸]]、[[王祺|王祺]]、[[朱蓉蓉|朱蓉蓉]]。<ref>{{cite news |author= |url=http://sc.sina.com.cn/news/tiyu/2014-12-04/detail-iawzunex4965998.shtml |title=《闯堂兔2》人物悉数亮相 堂堂也是马戏小能手 |newspaper=新浪 |accessdate=2015-01-10 |date=2014-12-04 |archive-date=2015-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150110091957/http://sc.sina.com.cn/news/tiyu/2014-12-04/detail-iawzunex4965998.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>该片在2015年[[元旦|元旦]]上映。<ref>{{cite news |author= |url=http://ent.qq.com/a/20141230/050526.htm |title=《闯堂兔2》蓄势待发 准备就绪只等上映 |newspaper=腾讯网 |accessdate=2015-01-10 |date=2014-12-30 |archive-date=2015-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150110101740/http://ent.qq.com/a/20141230/050526.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==剧情==
该片讲述马戏团小丑珊瑚与闯堂兔堂堂及他的伙伴们在闯堂镇斗智斗勇的故事。<ref>{{cite news |author= |url=http://yule.sohu.com/20140904/n404073998.shtml |title=《闯堂兔2疯狂马戏团》发海报 定档明年元旦 |newspaper=搜狐网 |accessdate=2015-01-10 |date=2014-09-04 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304224057/http://yule.sohu.com/20140904/n404073998.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

